<FONT size=-1 COLOR="#FFFF00"><b><u>Christmas 1985 Adverts</u></b></font></center><font size=-1 color="#ffffff">Featuring a long Woolworths advert with lots of vinyl albums - strange to see again! <b><i>(2:35)</i></b></font><center><font size=-2 color="#ffffff"><i>Watch full-sized <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DVnPvno6V9g" target="DVnPvno6V9g">at YouTube</a></font></center></TD></TR></TABLE><br></TD></TR></TABLE>
